Type locality: Galapagos. Lectotype BMNH 1975174 (
Breure 1979
). Distribution: Galápagos , Isla San Salvador ; it is only known from one population found in a small area near a natural fresh water source. There are probably no more than 200 individuals on a total range less than 1 km 2 (Parent 2003 ).

